  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Coordinated Liberia WASH Consortium Monitoring and Evaluation using Smartphones</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The five Liberia WASH consortium agencies will use smartphones to collect data for WASH consortium and bilaterally funded WASH projects.  The software and phones will be used for baseline, evaluation and monitoring data.  The WASH Consortium Coordination Team, will develop the data collection survey forms and manage and analyse the collected data.  Key activities will be the purchase of smartphones, the creation of monitoring forms, training of member agency staff and local government, a stakeholder learning event and a final evaluation workshop.</narrative>
  </description>
